---
import LinkedIn from './icons/linkedin.astro'
import Github from './icons/github.astro'
---
---
<article class="m-4 p-5 max-w-screen-md rounded-lg bg-principalCard flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:flex-row">
    <div>
        <picture>
            <img src="./avatarProgramming.jpg" alt="My photo " class="w-60 h-44 object-cover md:h-60 md:w-[43rem] rounded-lg">
        </picture>
        <div class="w-full h-10 my-4  flex justify-center">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lesliel-centeno/">
                <LinkedIn alt="Link to Leslie's LinkedIn account" class="w-8 h-8 text-proyectCard hover:scale-125"/>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/Leslie-L" class="px-2">
                <Github alt="Link to Leslie's Github account" class="w-8 h-8 text-proyectCard hover:scale-125" />
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-proyectCard md:ml-8">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Leslie Centeno</h1>
        <p>
            Passionate Systems Engineer with a Master's in Operations Research. I specialize in the art of problem-solving and fueled by challenging projects.
        </p>
        <p class="hidden md:block">
            I am genuinely excited about contributing my skills and enthusiasm to dynamic professional settings. Moreover, my overarching goal is to craft applications that are not only more accessible but also enhance the overall user experience. 
        </p>
        <p class="hidden md:block">
            I invite you to explore more about my work!
        </p>
    </div>
</article>